§ 8661. Classification The President may establish, and from time to time modify, as the needs of the service require, a classification of naval vessels. (Aug. 10, 1956, ch. 1041, 70A Stat. 448, § 7291; renumbered § 8661, Pub. L. 115–232, div. A, title VIII, § 807(d)(2), Aug. 13, 2018, 132 Stat. 1836.)
